{"tid":2397028,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"食環突然終止合約 支聯會年宵檔 30年來首取消","createTime":"2021-02-06T05:49:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T07:07:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"31ee6f1a79d8107473850ea4cefcfda10202fb87","tid":2397028,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T05:49:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210206/I57KTLXZWZEFJCKVI26UOXIKXM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210206%2FI57KTLXZWZEFJCKVI26UOXIKXM%2F&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMId4xWyFD0xakOW3kliQQxS8%3D&h=3244e19b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210206%2FI57KTLXZWZEFJCKVI26UOXIKXM%2F&h=82e689d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210206/I57KTLXZWZEFJCKVI26UOXIKXM/</a><br />\n<br />\n食環突然終止合約 支聯會年宵檔 30年來首取消<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1dag1QOOwiuDHhrwhGNYS2uFcd0=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LOYZZUOIDJHIBL3QM7SGL45U54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1dag1QOOwiuDHhrwhGNYS2uFcd0%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLOYZZUOIDJHIBL3QM7SGL45U54.jpg&h=2889ff78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■支聯會維園年宵攤位昨被食環署要求移除政治訊息，事後義工以橙布遮「平反六四」字眼。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政權持續打壓反對聲音，連年宵市場也不放過。支聯會一如以往今年在維園擺設年宵攤檔賣花，本報收到支聯會義工投訴，食環署指支聯會攤位展示政治訊息，與售賣鮮花無關，兩小時內須拆除相關橫額，否則「冚檔」。支聯會秘書蔡耀昌認為，該會擺年宵30年來相安無事，今次明顯是政治打壓。至凌晨12時半，支聯會年宵攤檔被食環署即時終止合約及要求今早7時交舖。支聯會主席李卓人指，今次是逾30年來首次被終止合約，批評「中共容不下任何異見聲音」。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會昨搭建攤位，掛起「平反六四 戰鬥到底」燈牌及「請捐款支持 六四集會案訴訟費」橫額，另一條橫額寫上「為自由 共命運 同抗爭」字眼，食環人員昨晚指攤位有「政治性字眼」，但未有指明哪一條橫額或字眼有問題，只着支聯會判斷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要求拆走政治標語<br />\n<br />\n食環人員晚上8時45分更在攤位貼上通告，指展示物品與獲准許售賣的鮮花無關，違反《使用協議》，要求兩小時內「移除所有政治性字眼」，否則「即時終止該協議，毋須交代原因」。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會本來由今日起，一連六日在維園年宵攤位售賣繡球花、太陽花等象徵自由民主的花束，「將民主、自由訊息帶進日常生活」，同時為支聯會籌備六四燭光集會被檢控的訴訟費用。<br />\n<br />\n有支聯會義工向本報指，由於。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李卓人回應指，這是支聯會逾30年來首次年宵被終止合約。他批評這在港版國安法下，中共要清洗所有政治反對聲音，「今次封殺係同整個政治大氣候有關，中共係容不下任何異見聲音」。<br />\n<br />\n他指，由於看不見中共會放鬆香港的高壓統治，支聯會的年宵料已成絕響。他指，日後或要改在私人地方舉辦，但一切言之尚早，今年的貨品或要轉售給其他人分銷。他指，不會就今次「封舖」尋求司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VLgPQzv-o7ZC0_S3HSC18FSs-FM=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QBMDHEH4LZAMJAKB4MRNACIV7E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVLgPQzv-o7ZC0_S3HSC18FSs-FM%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQBMDHEH4LZAMJAKB4MRNACIV7E.jpg&h=20418568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李卓人"},{"pid":"cdafac280e89cb6a93e3d9c4f50596667664184c","tid":2397028,"uid":42350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T05:51:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />天真嬌"},{"pid":"79295bbcd39cfe0ddb5c43be5bbeda7163ba2bec","tid":2397028,"uid":253016,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T05:52:21.000Z","msg":"平你老母六四咩"},{"pid":"3c89f56bdcc502ef0de3398f67579ce79fd4cb2d","tid":2397028,"uid":301952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T05:53:22.000Z","msg":"中華帝國主義 vs 大中華膠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94b4719d6f73effc09518d17f31d99891bb9b7a","tid":2397028,"uid":301989,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T05:55:42.000Z","msg":"傻閪支那會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b6350db15dcec68f62cecf3f4c32672b4d544c","tid":2397028,"uid":179007,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T05:57